                  Jiwoong (Andrew) Sohn
                </p>
                <p>
                  Hello. I'm a PhD Student at <a href="https://ethz.ch/en.html/">ETH Zürich</a>.<br><br>
                  I'm fortunate to be advised by  <a href="https://michaelmoor.me/">Prof. Michael Moor </a> at <a href="https://bsse.ethz.ch/mail">Medical AI Lab</a>.<br><br>
                  -
                </p>
                
                <p>
                  Previously, I obtained my Master's degree in Computer Science and Engineering at <a href="https://www.korea.edu/sites/en/index.do">Korea University</a> with early completion, where I was fortunate to be advised by <a href="https://scholar.google.co.kr/citations?user=RaBZafQAAAAJ&hl=ko">Prof. Jaewoo Kang</a>.
                  I work closely with <a href="https://scholar.google.co.kr/citations?user=rqBpumIAAAAJ&hl=en">Dr. Hyunjae Kim</a> in <a href="https://sites.google.com/view/qingyuchen/home/">Qingyu Chen's Lab</a>, and
                  <a href="https://scholar.google.com.hk/citations?user=gGcRkpYAAAAJ&hl=en">Xiangru Tang</a>, <a href="https://github.com/super-dainiu">Yanjun Shao</a> in the <a href="https://www.gersteinlab.org/">Gerstein Lab</a> 
                  at Yale University, where I was a research intern. I also work closely with <a href="https://ldi.khu.ac.kr/mujeen-sung-p-i">Prof. Mujeen Sung</a>, <a href="https://ireneli.eu/">Prof. Irene Li</a>, <a href="https://www.tomaszsternal.com/">Tomasz Sternal</a>, and <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jaehoon-yun-8994a9343/?locale=en_US">Jaehoon Yun</a>.
                </p>
                <p>
                  I’m always happy to connect and discuss about research.<br>
                  Feel free to <a href="" onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url: 'https://calendly.com/sohnji12/30min'});return false;">schedule a chat</a> or <a href="mailto:jisohn@ethz.ch">email me</a>! 😃
                </p>
              <td style="padding:1%;width:37%;max-width:37%;vertical-align:top;">
