      <h2>Research</h2>
      <p>
        I'm interested in natural language processing (NLP), large language models (LLMs), information retrieval (IR), and medical artificial intelligence (MAI). My research focuses on developing AI solutions that can make meaningful contributions to healthcare and medicine.
